== Ubiquity components ==

These packages make up the Ubiquity live installer.

 * ubiquity-frontend-gtk
 * ubiquity-ubuntu-artwork

Ubiquity needs full filesystem support for the partitioner.

 * xfsprogs
 * jfsutils
 * hfsplus [powerpc]  # ColinWatson
